  "remarks": "\nA subsidiary of IAIO within MODAFL. Manufactures, repairs and conducts overhauls of aeroplanes and aircraft engines and procures aviation related parts often of US origin typically via foreign intermediaries. IACI and its subsidiaries have also been detected using a worldwide network of brokers seeking to procure aviation related goods.",
